text: One of my engineers is getting this error on a freshly generated authentication. Any ideas how to resolve? I’m thinking it’s related to some sort Unix Epoch error since 19774 days ≈ 54 years ago ≈ 1970.
Yes, you can get this by using Chrome Developer Tools. Inspect the page, find the CSS file in the hs-fs folder and then right click, "copy link address"
